Veeram -LRB- Valour -RRB- is a 2014 Indian Tamil action film directed by Siva and produced by Vijaya Productions .
The film features Ajith Kumar in the lead role , while an ensemble supporting cast includes Tamannaah , Vidharth , Bala , Santhanam , Nassar , Pradeep Rawat and Abhinaya , among others .
Pre-production works had been ongoing since December 2011 , with shooting starting in April 2013 .
The film was released on 10 January 2014 .
The film received positive reviews from critics and became successful at box-office .
The film was dubbed and released in Telugu as Veerudokkade and in Hindi as Veeram The Powerman .
Despite the release of dubbed version , the film is being remade in Telugu as Katamarayudu -LRB- 2017 -RRB- with Pawan Kalyan .